5. **Median**: The median of these numbers is 151 (the average of the 5th and 6th numbers when sorted).
6. **Mode**: There is no mode since all numbers are unique.
7. **Distribution**: The numbers are prime and do not follow a simple arithmetic or geometric pattern.

These observations provide a basic statistical and numerical analysis of the given sets. [end of text]


